title: Loop hero and chill (channel update, AMA) [GOG]
author: Tim Ermilov
description:
Hi, I'm Tim.  
I do webdev, javascript and big data.
On this channel I want to teach you to build things using javascript. 
Sometimes I also play video games.

I (definitely) do weekly javascript news podcast and (trying to do) coding and gaming streams.

Want to contact me? Use yamalight@gmail.com 
Want to know more about my dev background? See http://codezen.net/

My Dev and Gaming System Specs:
CPU: i7-7700 @ 3.6ghz
RAM: Corsair Vengeance 32 GB @ 3200 MHz 
GPU: Gainward GeForce GTX 1070
SSDs: Samsung EVO 850 250GB + Intel 660p 1TB
HDDs: 1TB Seagate
OS: Windows 10 x64 Pro
Capture: Nvidia Share / OBS
Microphone: Blue Yeti Silver
